---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="General Tasks — Formic"
  description="Bimanual mobile manipulators and full humanoid robots — frontier hardware deployed under Formic Full Service."
  ogTitle="General Tasks"
  ogDescription="Bimanual mobile platforms and humanoid robots — the next frontier, on your floor now."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/general" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span>General Tasks
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">General Tasks</div>
    <h1>The <em>next frontier</em>,<br>on your floor now.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Bimanual mobile manipulators and full humanoid platforms — frontier hardware deployed, supported, and continuously upgraded under the Formic Full Service model. You get the upside; we carry the integration risk.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Why Now</div>
      <h2>General-purpose robotics is <em>finally shipping</em>.</h2>
      <p>For decades, general-task automation was the perpetual "five years away" of manufacturing. That changed. Bimanual mobile platforms are running production cycles in pilot programs today — and humanoid platforms are entering early customer trials.</p>
      <p>Formic is the deployment partner for mid-market manufacturers who want frontier capability without becoming a robotics R&amp;D shop themselves.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Pilot programs designed and run by Formic engineers</li>
        <li>Same Full Service model — fixed monthly price, no CapEx, all support included</li>
        <li>Continuous OTA upgrades as capability matures</li>
        <li>Direct line into vendor roadmaps</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Mobile bimanual manipulator on a production floor" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">General-task automation</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-9787.jpg" alt="Bimanual mobile manipulator at work" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Mobile · Bimanual</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — Mobile Bimanual Manipulator</div>
      <h2>Two arms, one base, <em>anywhere on the line</em>.</h2>
      <p>Bimanual mobile robots that handle multi-step manipulation tasks — bin picking, machine tending, assist work — and re-locate themselves between cells without a fixed footprint. Most useful where the work is too varied for fixed automation but too repetitive for skilled labor.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Bimanual manipulation for two-handed tasks</li>
        <li>Mobile base — relocates between cells throughout a shift</li>
        <li>Multi-step task chaining with vision and learned skills</li>
        <li>Available in pilot today; production rollouts in 2026</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Join a pilot →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">03 — Full Humanoids</div>
      <h2>Generalist robots, <em>deployed as a service</em>.</h2>
      <p>Full humanoid platforms for general-purpose manufacturing tasks — bin transfer, machine tending, assist work, and more. Covered by Formic Full Service, so you get the upside of frontier hardware with none of the integration risk.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Full Service-backed deployment of leading humanoid platforms</li>
        <li>Continuous capability upgrades over the lifetime of the agreement</li>
        <li>Shared learnings across the Formic customer base</li>
        <li>Currently in early access — limited slots available</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Apply for early access →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Humanoid robot platform" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Humanoid platforms</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Run frontier robots,<br><em>not frontier risk</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/" class="btn-ctawh">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
